== 球會生涯 ==
=== 巴素利 ===
扎卡於2002年加入[[巴塞爾足球俱樂部|巴塞爾]]的青訓，更在2008年便為[[巴塞爾足球俱樂部|巴塞爾]]U21上陣，3年間上陣37場，攻入11球<ref>{{NFT player|pid=43459}}</ref>。時任巴素利教練{{le|Thorsten Fink||芬克}}說:「[[杰尔丹·沙奇里|沙奇里]]為瑞士最佳的天才......但於扎卡之下。」<ref name="talent">{{cite web | url = http://www.goal.com/en-gb/news/2914/champions-league/2012/02/22/2921337/better-than-shaqiri-the-teenage-basel-star-who-bayern-munich | title = Better than Shaqiri – the teenage Basel star who Bayern Munich must stop tonight | publisher = Goal.com | accessdate = 2012-02-25 | date = 2012-02-22 | language = en | archive-date = 2012-02-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120225050221/http://www.goal.com/en-gb/news/2914/champions-league/2012/02/22/2921337/better-than-shaqiri-the-teenage-basel-star-who-bayern-munich | dead-url = no }}</ref>；而[[瑞士國家足球隊|瑞士國家足球隊]]教練[[奥特马·希茨费尔德|希茨费尔德]]則讚揚他為「年輕版的[[巴斯蒂安·施魏因斯泰格|施魏因斯泰格]]」<ref name="talent"/>。

從2010年起，扎卡為[[巴塞爾足球俱樂部|巴塞爾]]一線隊上陣。他於對陣[[迪比辛尼|迪比辛尼]]的[[欧洲冠军联赛|欧洲冠军联赛]]賽事中首次替巴素利上陣，同時射入1球，協助球隊以2比0勝出；在聯賽方面，他在對陣[[圖恩足球會|圖恩]]時射入首個聯賽入球。扎卡於2010-11賽季贏得聯賽冠軍，更於2011-12賽季獲得聯賽、盃賽雙料冠軍<ref name="sfv 1">{{cite web|url=http://www.fcb.ch/news/show/byItemID/de-de/10044/27863/26/7/7 |title=Der 15. Meistertitel für den FCB – die Bilanz einer grandiosen Saison |publisher=FC Basel 1893 |accessdate=2012-04-29 |date=2012-04-29 |language=de |last=Meister |first=Remo |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131016142727/http://www.fcb.ch/news/show/byItemID/de-de/10044/27863/26/7/7 |archivedate=2013-10-16 }}</ref><ref name="sfv 2">{{cite web|year=2012 |url=http://www.football.ch/sfv/chcup/de/telegramm.aspx?tg=1973921 |title=Matchtelegram FC Basel 1893 5:3 FC Luzern |publisher=football.ch |accessdate=2012-05-15 |language=de |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20121204154542/http://www.football.ch/sfv/chcup/de/telegramm.aspx?tg=1973921 |archivedate=2012-12-04 }}</ref>。

=== 慕遜加柏 ===
2012年5月18日，扎卡轉會至[[德國甲組足球聯賽|德國甲組足球聯賽]]球會[[门兴格拉德巴赫足球俱乐部|门兴格拉德巴赫]]，簽下5年合同，實際轉會費並沒有公佈，預計轉會費為850萬歐元<ref name="fcb4">{{cite web| url= http://www.fcb.ch/news/show/byItemID/de-de/10044/27987/26/7/7| title= Granit Xhaka wechselt im Sommer vom FCB zu Borussia Mönchengladbach| publisher= FC Basel 1893| accessdate= 2012-05-18| language= de| date= 2012-05-18| archive-url= https://archive.is/20130101110223/http://www.fcb.ch/news/show/byItemID/de-de/10044/27987/26/7/7| archive-date= 2013-01-01| dead-url= yes}}</ref>。

8月18日，扎卡在[[德國盃|德國盃]]中對陣[[亞琛足球俱樂部|亞琛]]時，首次為球隊上陣。在球隊的第二年，他為球隊正選上陣29次，後備入替5次；更於2014-15賽季正選上陣全部德甲賽事<ref name=kicker>{{cite news|url=http://www.kicker.de/news/fussball/bundesliga/vereine/2012-13/57343/vereinsspieler_xhaka-granit.html|title=Granit Xhaka|accessdate=2016-03-31|work=kicker|language=en|archive-date=2016-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160325161638/http://www.kicker.de/news/fussball/bundesliga/vereine/2012-13/57343/vereinsspieler_xhaka-granit.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。最終，該季球隊得第3名，獲得歐聯資格，而他本人亦被選為德甲最佳陣容其中一員<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bundesliga.de/de/liga/news/infografik-die-top-11-der-saison.jsp|title=Infografik: Die Top-11 der Saison 2014/15|date=2015-05-25|accessdate=2015-05-25|work=Bundesliga|language=de|archive-date=2015-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150717111132/http://www.bundesliga.de/de/liga/news/infografik-die-top-11-der-saison.jsp|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年12月20日，扎卡於聯賽對陣[[達斯泰特98體育會|達斯泰特98]]時，在上半場時故意踢對手，拿到了在效力慕遜加柏期間的第五張紅牌。事後，他捐出20,000歐元以作道歉<ref>{{cite news|title=Granit Xhaka pays his dues after Gladbach star racks up red cards|url=http://www.espnfc.co.uk/blog/the-toe-poke/65/post/2767083/gladbach-xhaka-pays-after-red-cards|accessdate=2016-06-22|publisher=ESPN FC|date=2015-12-22|language=en|archive-date=2016-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160119222425/http://www.espnfc.co.uk/blog/the-toe-poke/65/post/2767083/gladbach-xhaka-pays-after-red-cards|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 阿仙奴 ===
2016年5月25日，扎卡轉投[[阿森纳足球俱乐部|阿森纳]]，轉會費4500萬歐元，將會穿上29號球衣<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-3608536/Granit-Xhaka-signs-Arsenal-35m-deal-Arsene-Wenger-admits-club-tracking-Swiss-midfielder-long-time.html|title=Granit Xhaka signs for Arsenal in £35m deal as Arsene Wenger admits club have been tracking Swiss midfielder 'for a long time'|publisher=Daily Mail|date=2016-05-25|accessdate=2016-05-25|language=en|archive-date=2016-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160902004653/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-3608536/Granit-Xhaka-signs-Arsenal-35m-deal-Arsene-Wenger-admits-club-tracking-Swiss-midfielder-long-time.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Granit Xhaka signs for Arsenal: Gunners complete deal for Swiss international midfielder |url=http://www.standard.co.uk/sport/football/granit-xhaka-signs-for-arsenal-gunners-complete-deal-for-swiss-international-midfielder-a3251411.html |newspaper=London Evening Standard |first=James |last=Benge |date=2016-05-25 |accessdate=2016-05-25 |language=en |archive-date=2016-05-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160525114927/http://www.standard.co.uk/sport/football/granit-xhaka-signs-for-arsenal-gunners-complete-deal-for-swiss-international-midfielder-a3251411.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title=Arsenal will pay around £30m for Granit Xhaka, Sky Sports News HQ understands |url=http://www.skysports.com/football/news/11670/10290914/arsenal-will-pay-around-16330m-for-granit-xhaka-sky-sports-news-hq-understands |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2016-05-22 |accessdate=2016-05-25 |language=en |archive-date=2016-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160524211019/http://www.skysports.com/football/news/11670/10290914/arsenal-will-pay-around-16330m-for-granit-xhaka-sky-sports-news-hq-understands |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他於友誼賽對陣[[美國職業足球大聯盟|美國職業足球大聯盟]]聯隊時，首次披上阿仙奴球衣。他於半場時後備入替，最終阿仙奴以2比1贏下比賽<ref>{{Cite news|title=MLS All-Stars 1-2 Arsenal - Report|url=http://www.arsenal.com/match/report/1617/post/first-team/mls-all-stars-1-2-arsenal-report|publisher=Arsenal.com|date=2016-07-29|accessdate=2016-07-30|language=en|archive-date=2016-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160730181509/http://www.arsenal.com/match/report/1617/post/first-team/mls-all-stars-1-2-arsenal-report|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

扎卡於對陣[[利物浦足球會|利物浦]]時首次為阿仙奴上陣，於66分鐘後備入替[[穆罕默德·艾兰尼|-{zh-hans:艾兰尼; zh-hk:艾蘭尼;zh-tw:艾蘭尼;}-]]，他在比賽中拿下1張黃牌，阿仙奴亦以3比4落敗<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.bbc.com/sport/football/37001073|title= Arsenal 3-4 Liverpool|website= BBC|date= 2016-08-14|accessdate= 2016-08-16|first= Saj|last= Chowdhury|language= en|archive-date= 2016-08-15|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160815043340/http://www.bbc.com/sport/football/37001073|dead-url= no}}</ref>。9月17日，在聯賽對陣[[赫尔城足球俱乐部|赫尔城]]的比賽時，扎卡於35碼外射入加盟後首球，最終球隊大勝4比1<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/37326798|title= Hull City 1-4 Arsenal|publisher= BBC Sport|date= 2016-07-17|accessdate= 2016-09-17|language= en|archive-date= 2016-09-17|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160917154144/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/37326798|dead-url= no}}</ref>。4天後，扎卡於[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]對陣[[诺丁汉森林足球俱乐部|诺丁汉森林]]時，再次於35碼外攻入一記遠射，協助球隊大勝4比0，晉級賽事的第4圈<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/fa-league-cups/nottingham-forest-vs-arsenal-match-report-granit-xhaka-goal-lucas-perez-arsene-wenger-result-efl-cup-a7319556.html|title=Nottingham Forest vs Arsenal report: Granit Xhaka and Lucas Perez give Arsene Wenger plenty to smile about|date=2016-09-21|accessdate=2016-09-21|work=The Independent|language=en|archive-date=2016-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160923092523/http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/fa-league-cups/nottingham-forest-vs-arsenal-match-report-granit-xhaka-goal-lucas-perez-arsene-wenger-result-efl-cup-a7319556.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。扎卡在對陣[[斯旺西城足球俱乐部|斯旺西]]時，於第70分鐘侵犯對方翼鋒{{link-en|莫度·巴路|Modou Barrow}}而被罰紅牌離場，但阿仙奴仍能以3比2險勝<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/football/37594169|title=Arsenal 3-2 Swansea City|website=BBC|date=2016-09-24|accessdate=2016-09-24|language=en|archive-date=2016-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161014164400/http://www.bbc.com/sport/football/37594169|dead-url=no}}</ref>。5月7日，扎卡在對陣[[曼聯|曼聯]]時攻入一球，協助阿仙奴以2比0勝出，終結對手25場聯賽不敗紀錄<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.bbc.com/sport/football/39760508|title= Arsenal 2-0 Manchester United|publisher= BBC Sport|date= 2017-05-07|accessdate= 2017-05-07|language= en|archive-date= 2017-05-06|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20170506233512/http://www.bbc.com/sport/football/39760508|dead-url= no}}</ref>。

扎卡於參與了[[2017年英格兰足总杯决赛|2017年英格兰足总杯决赛]]對陣[[車路士足球會|車路士]]的比賽，他正選上陣，協助球隊以2比1勝出奪冠<ref name=FACup>{{cite web|url= https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=WXeS3rsW1Z8|title= Arsenal 2–1 Chelsea – Emirates FA Cup Final 2016/17|via=YouTube|publisher=FATV|language= en}}</ref>。他亦參與了[[2017年英格蘭社區盾|2017年英格蘭社區盾]]的比賽，最終阿仙奴以[[互射十二碼|互射十二碼]]的形式贏得冠軍<ref name=CS>{{cite web|url= https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=sVwr6MxovYQ|title= Arsenal 1–1 Chelsea (4–1 Pens) – FA Community Shield|via= YouTube|publisher= FATV|language= en|accessdate= 2018-03-19|archive-date= 2020-04-01|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200401032240/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sVwr6MxovYQ&app=desktop|dead-url= no}}</ref>。12月22日，扎卡在對陣[[利物浦足球會|利物浦]]的聯賽中，於25碼外射入一球，最終雙方以3比3握手言和<ref>{{cite web|url= https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/42362392|title= Arsenal 3–3 Liverpool|publisher= BBC|date= 2017-12-22|accessdate= 2018-01-09|language= en|archive-date= 2017-12-22|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20171222010916/http://www.bbc.com/sport/football/42362392|dead-url= no}}</ref>。1月24日，扎卡於英格蘭聯賽盃主場對陣[[車路士足球會|車路士]]的比賽中取得入球，助球隊以2比1的比數晉身決賽<ref>{{cite web|url= https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/42713408|title= Arsenal 2–1 Chelsea|publisher= BBC|date= 2018-01-24|accessdate= 2018-01-24|language= en|archive-date= 2018-01-24|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20180124003359/http://www.bbc.com/sport/football/42713408|dead-url= no}}</ref>。3月15日，他於[[欧足联欧洲联赛|欧足联欧洲联赛]]對陣[[AC米蘭|AC米蘭]]次回合的比賽中遠射得手，助球隊於主場以3比1勝出<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.bbc.com/sport/football/43406580|title= Arsenal 3 - 1 AC Milan|language= en|work= BBC|date= 2018-03-15|accessdate= 2018-03-15|archive-date= 2018-03-15|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20180315173154/http://www.bbc.com/sport/football/43406580|dead-url= no}}</ref>。

2018年9月23日，在阿森纳和[[埃弗顿足球俱乐部|埃弗顿]]的比赛中，扎卡迎来代表阿森纳出场的第100场比赛。<ref>{{cite web |title=ARSENAL VS. EVERTON  2 - 0|url=https://uk.soccerway.com/matches/2018/09/23/england/premier-league/arsenal-fc/everton-football-club/2795319/ |website=Soccerway |date=2018-09-23}}</ref>

2021年2月2日，在阿森纳對陣[[伍尔弗汉普顿流浪足球俱乐部|狼隊]]的客場比赛中，扎卡迎来代表阿森纳出场的第200场比赛。<ref>{{cite web|url= https://www.marca.com/futbol/premier-league/wolves-arsenal-directo/2021/02/02/01_0106_20210202_39_3.html|title= Wolves - Arsenal · Premier League|publisher= [[馬卡報|馬卡報]]|accessdate= 2021-02-02|language= es|archive-date= 2021-02-02|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210202175152/https://www.marca.com/futbol/premier-league/wolves-arsenal-directo/2021/02/02/01_0106_20210202_39_3.html|dead-url= no}}</ref>

== 國家隊生涯 ==
[[File:Suisse_vs_Argentine_-_Granit_Xhaka_&_Lionel_Messi.jpg|thumb]]（右）]]
扎卡曾代表[[瑞士|瑞士]]各階青年國家隊上陣，其中於U17國家隊，他參加2009年的[[U17世界盃足球賽|U17世界盃足球賽]]，最終瑞士亦贏得冠軍。扎卡雙親為[[阿爾巴尼亞|阿爾巴尼亞]]籍，他能選擇為出生地瑞士或祖國阿爾巴尼亞的國家隊上陣。由於他認為阿爾巴尼亞足總忽視他而瑞士足總歡迎他，因此他選擇代表瑞士上陣。

===2012年歐國盃===
2011年，他於2012歐國盃外圍賽以2比2戰和英格蘭的比賽中完成成年國家隊首秀。而在對[[盧森堡|盧森堡]]的賽事，攻入在國家隊的首個入球，令瑞士以1比0小勝。可惜瑞士未能在外圍賽出線。

===2012年夏季奧林匹克運動會===
2012年，瑞士曾經嘗試邀請扎卡為國出戰奧運，可惜球員傾向留在球會進行季前集訓，拒絕邀請<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/07/09/oly-socc-swiss-squad-idUSB29215720120709 | title = Olympics-Shaqiri, Xhaka excluded from Swiss soccer squad | publisher = reuters.com | date = 2012-07-09 | accessdate = 2012-07-27 | language = en | archive-date = 2014-04-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140407093229/http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/07/09/oly-socc-swiss-squad-idUSB29215720120709 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

===2014年世界盃===
扎卡上陣了全部10場世界盃外圍賽的比賽，更在對陣[[斯洛文尼亞國家足球隊|斯洛文尼亞國家足球隊]]的兩場比賽皆有進球<ref name=fifa>{{cite news|url= https://www.fifa.com/worldcup/players/player=311558/played-matches.html|title= Granit XHAKA|accessdate= 2014-06-21|language= en|publisher= FIFA|archive-date= 2014-06-19|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140619085859/http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/players/player=311558/played-matches.html|dead-url= no}}</ref>。於2014年世界盃中，扎卡於負法國5比2的比賽中有一球進帳<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/25285207|title=Switzerland 2-5 France|date=2014-06-20|accessdate=2014-06-21|work=BBC|language=en|archive-date=2016-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160121002005/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/25285207|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===2016年歐國盃===
扎卡獲選為2016年歐國盃瑞士陣容的其中一員，同組的對手包括祖國[[阿爾巴尼亞|阿爾巴尼亞]]，他哥哥杜倫·沙加也在陣中。格列·沙加及杜倫·沙加均正選上陣，瑞士最終小勝1比0。而兩兄弟的母親則在場邊，穿起印有半張瑞士國旗及半張阿爾巴尼亞國旗的衣服觀戰<ref>{{cite news|last1=Gill|first1=Kieran|title=Granit and Taulant Xhaka go head to head at Euro 2016... as their mother wears a half-and-half Switzerland-Albania shirt and older brother throws a tantrum on the touchline|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-3636643/Granit-Taulant-Xhaka-head-head-Euro-2016-mother-wears-half-half-Switzerland-Albania-shirt-older-brother-throws-tantrum-touchline.html|accessdate=2016-06-11|work=Daily Mail|date=2016-06-11|language=en|archive-date=2016-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160611160656/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-3636643/Granit-Taulant-Xhaka-head-head-Euro-2016-mother-wears-half-half-Switzerland-Albania-shirt-older-brother-throws-tantrum-touchline.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。賽後，他獲選為賽事最佳球員<ref>{{cite news|last1= Atkin|first1= John|title= Switzerland hold on against ten-man Albania|url= http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuro/season=2016/matches/round=2000448/match=2017878/postmatch/report/index.html|accessdate= 2016-06-25|language= en|publisher= UEFA|date= 2016-06-11|archive-date= 2016-06-11|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160611180324/http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuro/season=2016/matches/round=2000448/match=2017878/postmatch/report/index.html|dead-url= no}}</ref>。而在對[[波蘭國家足球隊|波蘭國家足球隊]]的比賽中，雙方於法定時間以1比1打平，需以[[互射十二碼|互射十二碼]]分勝負；可是，扎卡射失了十二碼，使瑞士以4比5落敗，在16強出局<ref>{{cite news|last1=Brassell|first1=Andy|title=Poland hold nerve after Switzerland's Granit Xhaka blazes penalty wide|url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2016/jun/25/switzerland-poland-euro-2016-match-report|accessdate=2016-06-25|language=en|work=The Guardian|date=2016-06-25|archive-date=2020-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200801041625/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2016/jun/25/switzerland-poland-euro-2016-match-report|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===2018年世界盃===
於[[2018年國際足協世界盃外圍賽_(歐洲區)|2018年國際足協世界盃外圍賽]]舉行前，有猜測指扎卡將會轉為效力於2016年5月被[[歐洲足球協會聯盟|歐洲足球協會聯盟]]和[[国际足球联合会|国际足球联合会]]承認的[[科索沃國家足球隊|科索沃國家足球隊]]。可是，扎卡其後發表公開信，指出因他於[[2016年歐洲國家盃|2016年歐洲國家盃]]中曾為瑞士隊上陣，因此不符合資格改效科索沃隊<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://talentet.eu/2016/08/30/leter-e-hapur-nga-granit-xhaka/|title=Letër e hapur nga Granit XHAKA – TALENTËT|website=talentet.eu|access-date=2016-09-06|language=de|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160905024345/http://talentet.eu/2016/08/30/leter-e-hapur-nga-granit-xhaka/|archive-date=2016-09-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

扎卡獲選為2018年世界盃瑞士陣容的其中一員<ref>{{cite news |title=2018 World Cup: Switzerland name Granit Xhaka and Xherdan Shaqiri in squad |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/44360966 |accessdate=2018-06-22 |language=en |publisher=BBC Sport |date=2018-06-04 |archive-date=2019-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190330223737/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/44360966 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。6月22日，他在對陣[[塞爾維亞國家足球隊|塞爾維亞國家足球隊]]時，以一記遠射板平比分，協助球隊以2比1反勝對手。扎卡和另一位入球球員[[杰尔丹·沙奇里|沙奇里]]皆有科索沃血統，於慶祝時做出[[双头鹰|双头鹰]]的手勢，與[[阿爾巴尼亞國旗|阿爾巴尼亞國旗]]相似<ref>{{cite news |last1=Lowe |first1=Sid |title=Switzerland’s Xherdan Shaqiri stuns Serbia with late breakaway |url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2018/jun/22/serbia-switzerland-xherdan-shaqiri-world-cup-group-e-match-report |accessdate=2018-06-22 |language=en |work=The Guardian |date=2018-06-22 |quote=As he turned and screamed, he took his shirt off, flexed his muscles and performed a double-eagle celebration, a recreation of the Albanian flag. Alongside him, Granit Xhaka did the same – for the second time. |archive-date=2020-04-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200401235602/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2018/jun/22/serbia-switzerland-xherdan-shaqiri-world-cup-group-e-match-report |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Swiss duo's 'provocative' black eagle goal celebration 'mixes sport and politics' |url=https://edition.cnn.com/2018/06/23/football/xherdan-shaqiri-granit-xhaka-eagle-goal-celebration-serbia-switzerland-world-cup-spt-intl/index.html |accessdate=2018-06-25 |publisher=CNN |date=2018-06-24 |language=en |archive-date=2019-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191207080428/https://edition.cnn.com/2018/06/23/football/xherdan-shaqiri-granit-xhaka-eagle-goal-celebration-serbia-switzerland-world-cup-spt-intl/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Switzerland's Xhaka and Shaqiri charged by Fifa over Serbia goal celebrations |url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2018/jun/23/xhaka-and-shaqiri-goal-celebrations-bring-balkan-politics-to-world-cup |accessdate=2018-06-24 |publisher=The Guardian |date=2018-06-25 |language=en |archive-date=2020-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200518124916/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2018/jun/23/xhaka-and-shaqiri-goal-celebrations-bring-balkan-politics-to-world-cup |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=World Cup 2018: Xherdan Shaqiri and Granit Xhaka’s controversial goal celebrations criticised by Swiss media |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/world-cup/world-cup-2018-switzerland-serbia-granit-xhaka-xherdan-shaqiri-goal-celebrations-why-controversial-a8413426.html |accessdate=2018-06-25 |publisher=The Guardian |date=2018-06-23 |language=en |archive-date=2019-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191207083444/https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/world-cup/world-cup-2018-switzerland-serbia-granit-xhaka-xherdan-shaqiri-goal-celebrations-why-controversial-a8413426.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。之後因為該行為，被罰款10000[[瑞士法郎|瑞士法郎]]<ref>{{cite news |title=World Cup 2018: Switzerland trio avoid bans for 'eagle gesture' goal celebrations |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/44606965 |accessdate=2018-06-25 |language=en |publisher=BBC Sport |date=2018-06-25 |archive-date=2020-06-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200623203829/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/44606965 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title= World Cup 2018: Granit Xhaka and Xherdan Shaqiri avoid bans after political goal celebrations |language= en |url= https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/world-cup/world-cup-2018-granit-xhaka-xherdan-shaqiri-goal-celebrations-albania-kosovo-serbia-fine-a8416466.html |accessdate= 2018-06-25 |publisher= BBC Sport |date= 2018-06-25 |archive-date= 2020-04-01 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200401235614/https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/world-cup/world-cup-2018-granit-xhaka-xherdan-shaqiri-goal-celebrations-albania-kosovo-serbia-fine-a8416466.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

===2020年歐國盃===
2021年6月28日，扎卡在[[羅馬尼亞|羅馬尼亞]][[國家體育場_(布加勒斯特)|國家體育場]]進行的[[2020年歐洲國家盃|2020年歐洲國家盃]]16強賽中為[[馬里奧·加夫拉諾維奇|馬里奧·加夫拉諾維奇]]的進球送出了助攻，這讓比賽進入了加時賽，最終點球大戰瑞士隊獲勝，成功晉級八強，扎卡以92%傳球成功率、100%長傳成功率、13次關鍵傳球、1次助攻，獲得本場最佳球員。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.abola.pt/nnh/2021-06-28/euro-2020-xhaka-eleito-o-melhor-em-campo-no-franca-suica/895963 |title=XHAKA ELEITO O MELHOR EM CAMPO NO FRANÇA – SUÍÇA |date=2021-06-28 |work=A BOLA |accessdate=2021-06-28 |archive-date=2021-07-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210704033154/https://abola.pt/nnh/2021-06-28/euro-2020-xhaka-eleito-o-melhor-em-campo-no-franca-suica/895963 |dead-url=no }}</ref>  

